Functional requirements:
--> The system must allow users to introduce expenses or incomes
    --> The system must allow users to choose from different categories and after that, input details like: price,date,custom details.
--> The system must allow users to see their curretn balance
--> The systen must allow users to modify an older record
--> The system must allow users to view all the records

Non-functional requirments:
--> The system should allow users to automatically choose the current date ( Functionality ).
--> The system sould allow users to sort the records by amount, date, etc ( Functionality ).
--> The system should feature a simplistic design ( Utility ).
--> The system should be available 24/7 ( Reliability ).
--> The system should display error messages if the user gets something wrong ( Serviceability ).